    "title": "McDonald's India Consulting Pvt Ltd is Hiring: Guest Relations Manager (Lead)",
    "description": "Grow your career with McDonald's India Consulting Pvt Ltd! We are hiring a Guest Relations Manager for our Nagpur team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout McDonald's India Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nMcDonald's India Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nagpur, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with McDonald's India Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
